{"type":"answer","id":273024,"parentType":"question","parentId":25919,"uid":48814,"contents":"电影上第一次运用了蒙太奇手法(战舰波将金号)。建筑风格上，其实斯大林式建筑还挺美观的，我挺喜欢 (参考下图)。但赫鲁晓夫式公寓楼就很丑，深远影响了中国早期楼房。普通审美上苏联共产风把中国带往恶俗的道路上一路狂奔，比如各种红黄搭配，从店面招牌到大灯笼到国旗到国徽，浓浓的乡土暴发户既视感。<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/dPJEuwx.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/dPJEuwx.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/dPJEuwx.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/wt3oqhz.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/wt3oqhz.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/wt3oqhz.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a>","date":"2020-05-24","agreeCount":1,"discussionCount":1}